    "created_at": "2015-09-30T05:34:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-30T05:34:58Z",
    "body": "After some testing I think it is not a bug of Notification, but from something else.\n\nTo verify that you can create a notification in Slack by sending slackbot a `/remind me in 2s to notify`, and then print the number of connections to Xorg with `sudo lsof | grep /tmp/.X11-unix/X0 | wc -l`. And you can find that the number doesn't change when the notification shows and disapears.\n"
  },
